## Customize tbl_summary() output {auto-animate="true"}


::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code}
tbl_summary(
  sm_trial,
  by = trt,
  type = age ~ "continuous2",
  statistic = 
    list(
      age ~ c("{mean} ({sd})", 
              "{min}, {max}"), 
      response ~ "{n} / {N} ({p}%)"
    ),
  label = 
    grade ~ "Pathologic tumor grade",
  digits = age ~ 1
)
```

